1. *Rukavice* su mi omiljeni zimski modni dodatak. (Gloves are my favorite winter fashion accessory.)
2. Molim vas da obučete *rukavice* prije ulaska u bolnicu. (Please put on gloves before entering the hospital.)
3. *Rukavice* su vrlo važne za zaštitu ruku prilikom rada s kemikalijama. (Gloves are very important for protecting hands when working with chemicals.)
4. Da li si vidio moje *rukavice*? (Have you seen my gloves?)
5. Ove *rukavice* su izrađene od najfinije kože. (These gloves are made of the finest leather.)
6. Bez *rukavica*, ruke će vam se smrznuti na ovim temperaturama. (Without gloves, your hands will freeze in these temperatures.)
7. U prodavnici sam kupio nove *rukavice* za skijanje. (I bought new ski gloves at the store.)
8. Izgubio sam jednu *rukavicu*, pa sada imam samo jednu. (I lost one glove, so now I only have one.)
9. *Rukavice* su mu skliznule s ruku dok je vozio bicikl. (His gloves slipped off his hands while he was riding his bike.)
10. Moram prati svoje *rukavice* jer su se zaprljale. (I have to wash my gloves because they got dirty.)